#. <section class="sutta" id="an7.79"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.79:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.79:0.2"
msgid "8. Vinayavagga"
msgstr "8. The Monastic Law"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.79:0.3"
msgid "79. Paṭhamavinayadharasobhanasutta"
msgstr "79. Shines as an Expert in the Monastic Law (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.142"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: samannāgato → samannāgato bhikkhu (bj, s1-3, mr)
msgctxt "an7.79:1.1"
msgid "“Sattahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato vinayadharo sobhati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, a mendicant with seven qualities shines as an expert in the "
"monastic law."

msgctxt "an7.79:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi sattahi?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "an7.79:1.3"
msgid "Āpattiṃ jānāti, "
msgstr "They know what is an offence. "

msgctxt "an7.79:1.4"
msgid "anāpattiṃ jānāti, "
msgstr "They know what is not an offence. "

msgctxt "an7.79:1.5"
msgid "lahukaṃ āpattiṃ jānāti, "
msgstr "They know what is a light offence. "

msgctxt "an7.79:1.6"
msgid "garukaṃ āpattiṃ jānāti, "
msgstr "They know what is a serious offence. "

msgctxt "an7.79:1.7"
msgid "sīlavā hoti … pe … samādāya sikkhati sikkhāpadesu, "
msgstr ""
"They’re ethical, restrained in the code of conduct, with appropriate "
"behavior and means of collecting alms; seeing danger in the slightest flaw, "
"they keep the rules they’ve undertaken. "

msgctxt "an7.79:1.8"
msgid ""
"catunnaṃ jhānānaṃ ābhicetasikānaṃ nikāmalābhī hoti akicchalābhī "
"akasiralābhī, "
msgstr ""
"They get the four absorptions—blissful meditations in the present life that "
"belong to the higher mind—when they want, without trouble or difficulty. "

msgctxt "an7.79:1.9"
msgid "āsavānaṃ khayā … pe … sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"They realize the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in this "
"very life, and live having realized it with their own insight due to the end "
"of defilements."

msgctxt "an7.79:1.10"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, sattahi dhammehi samannāgato vinayadharo sobhatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant with these seven qualities shines as an expert in the monastic "
"law.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.79:1.11"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
